               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Saint Peter, ጸሎተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡; Book of the Disciples, መጽሐፈ፡ አርድእት፡; Treatise on the Trinity,  ዜና: ሥላሴ:; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="6v" facs="006">Fols 1r–6v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4668Prayer">Protective prayers
